OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1774026671
OL,3,CTube strike called off after
OL,4,C'progress' in talks between union and
OL,5,Cmanagement
OL,7,FTwo 24-hour strikes next week by
OL,8,FLondon Underground drivers have been
OL,9,Fcalled off after progress in talks
OL,10,Fover hours, but further planned
OL,11,Fwalkouts remain on.
OL,13,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,14,FTransport union (RMT) were due to
OL,15,Fstrike from 12pm next Tuesday and
OL,16,Fagain for 24 hours from noon next
OL,17,FThursday.
