OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1774026671
OL,3,CTube strike called off after
OL,4,C'progress' in talks between union and
OL,5,Cmanagement
OL,7,FThe union is in dispute over changes
OL,8,Fto the working week, but it said
OL,9,Fprogress had been made in talks with
OL,10,FLondon Underground management.
OL,12,FThe RMT said the dispute over a
OL,13,Fcondensed hours four-day week for Tube
OL,14,Fdrivers is "far from over", but LU
OL,15,Fmanagement have taken "steps in the
OL,16,Fright direction".
OL,18,FFurther talks are planned in the
OL,19,Fcoming days and weeks to try and reach
OL,20,Fa negotiated settlement.
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@ZO]wD@WOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
