OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1774026671
OL,3,CTube strike called off after
OL,4,C'progress' in talks between union and
OL,5,Cmanagement
OL,7,FOther strike dates in April and May
OL,8,Fremain in place and additional action
OL,9,Fon June 16 and 18 is planned.
OL,11,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,12,Fsaid: "Through our show of industrial
OL,13,Fstrength and unity, we have forced
OL,14,Fmanagement into a position where they
OL,15,Fare now willing to seriously engage
OL,16,Fwith the issues our members want
OL,17,Faddressing.
OL,19,F"Further talks will take place and the
OL,20,Fdispute remains live."
OL,26,@tD@GOU{D@AOU|D@VO]
